title: Europe Union probes Elon Musk’s X over handling of Israel-Gaza war
description: EU commissioner Thierry Breton has pressed Musk over the company’s handling of illegal content and disinformation related to the Hamas attacks against Israel.

title: Montana federal judge voices doubt over state’s TikTok ban
description: District Judge Donald Molloy said Montana had not substantiated its claims that TikTok users’ data was being “stolen” or misused.

title: Worried about the 23andMe hack? Here’s what you can do.
description: A hacker offered to sell information on 23andme’s millions of users, calling out Jewish people specifically. Here’s how to ask the company to delete your data.

title: Hamas vows to broadcast hostage executions. Tech firms can’t stop them.
description: Live-streamed murders in Buffalo, N.Y., and Christchurch, New Zealand, remain visible on the web long after the mass killings took place.
